MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

95-22. First Natl. Supermarkets, Inc. v. Merrill Lynch, Pierce, Fenner & Smith, Inc.

Cuyahoga County, No. 66454. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted, effective January 31,1996.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
